                     <interp inst="t17930911-115-person1213" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>I am the clerk of Stockton parish; I have the book of marriages there.</p>
               <p>Q. Be so good as to produce it and turn to the entry of the 8th of January, 1789. (Reads.)</p>
               <p>No. 864, 
               <persName id="t17930911-115-person1214">
                  Matthew
                   Miller
